# Build artifacts NEVER belong in the repo (vite watcher + git hygiene). This
# crate builds with CARGO_TARGET_DIR pointed OUTSIDE the repo tree; these lines
# are defence-in-depth in case someone builds with the default target dir.
/target/
target/
**/*.wasm
*.rlib
*.rmeta
# Cargo.lock IS committed (binary-ish crate: reproducible dep graph for the cutover).
